  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433870/extras/996df6b19db268adb3a48f8f7f53f1df.poster.avif?t=1636391092\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433870/extras/996df6b19db268adb3a48f8f7f53f1df.webm?t=1636391092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433870/extras/996df6b19db268adb3a48f8f7f53f1df.mp4?t=1636391092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A knight, a mysterious cat and a castle where the whole scenario is dynamically modified, creating rooms and rooms with incredible challenges to overcome.<br><br>Brick to Me puts you on a Puzzle Platform full of dynamically arranged rooms with a random path to the confrontation with “Space Mania”.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Over 60 rooms randomly assembled<br></li><li> Intriguing puzzles<br></li><li> A kitten that needs be peted<br></li><li> A boomerange to defeat enemies<br></li><li> A very unusual boss fight<br></li><li> Enter into Bricky to Me and try to escape from this random castle</li></ul>",
